Album_Content: Something short and leading about the collection below—its contents, the creator, etc. Make it short and sweet, but not too short so folks don't simply skip over it entirely.
Card_Content: This is a media card. You can use this section to describe the content.
Footer_Content: Something here to give the footer a purpose!
Home_Top_Head: Title of a longer featured blog post
Home_Top_Content: Multiple lines of text that form the lede, informing new readers quickly and efficiently about what's most interesting in this post's contents.
PostBody1: This is a wider card with supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content.
